<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFItzykson.2C_Claude_and_Zuber.2C_Jean_Bernard1980">Itzykson, Claude and Zuber, Jean Bernard (1980). <i>Quantum Field Theory</i>. McGraw-Hill International Book Co.,. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0070320713" class="internal">ISBN 0-07-032071-3</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Quantum+Field+Theory&amp;rft.aulast=Itzykson%2C+Claude+and+Zuber%2C+Jean+Bernard&amp;rft.au=Itzykson%2C+Claude+and+Zuber%2C+Jean+Bernard&amp;rft.date=1980&amp;rft.pub=McGraw-Hill+International+Book+Co.%2C&amp;rft.isbn=0-07-032071-3&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Quantum_field_theory"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREF.5B.5BNikolay_Bogoliubov.7CBogoliubov.2C_Nikolay.5D.5D.2C_.5B.5BDmitry_Shirkov.7CShirkov.2C_Dmitry.5D.5D1982"><a href="/wiki/Nikolay_Bogoliubov" title="Nikolay Bogoliubov" class="mw-redirect">Bogoliubov, Nikolay</a>, <a href="/wiki/Dmitry_Shirkov" title="Dmitry Shirkov">Shirkov, Dmitry</a> (1982). <i>Quantum Fields</i>. Benjamin-Cummings Pub. Co. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0805309837" class="internal">ISBN 0805309837</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Quantum+Fields&amp;rft.aulast=%5B%5BNikolay+Bogoliubov%7CBogoliubov%2C+Nikolay%5D%5D%2C+%5B%5BDmitry+Shirkov%7CShirkov%2C+Dmitry%5D%5D&amp;rft.au=%5B%5BNikolay+Bogoliubov%7CBogoliubov%2C+Nikolay%5D%5D%2C+%5B%5BDmitry+Shirkov%7CShirkov%2C+Dmitry%5D%5D&amp;rft.date=1982&amp;rft.pub=Benjamin-Cummings+Pub.+Co&amp;rft.isbn=0805309837&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Quantum_field_theory"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
